# ============================================================================
# zen-markdown-themes .gitignore
#
# Principle: ship the products, keep process material private.
# Polished CSS themes, docs, and the preview tool are public, in git.
# Reference material, design notes, drafts, and handoffs are private: kept out
# of version control and synced across machines via cloud storage.
# ============================================================================

